Patrick Housen
Welcome to my digital portfolio! My name is Patrick Housen (1990), Belgian composer - soundartist - guitarist residing in Ghent. Passion for composing, creating, crafting, playing (live), developing, listening to, trying to understand and discovering (New) Sounds and Music!

Musica Futurista (1) by MATRIX New Music Centre

MATRIX New Music Centre / SoundCloud
Some results of our workshop 'Musica Futurista' at Jeugdhuis Den Eglantier, Sint-Niklaas (BE). 'Musica Futurista' is a workshop series on experimental musical instruments, developed by MATRIX New Music Centre Special thanks to Mattias Parent (Logos Foundation) and Patrick Housen (composer) More info: matrix-new-music.be/musica-futurista

HomebushBay

Sarah Rathé / Vimeo
Homebush Bay revolves around the atmosphere of loneliness and confusion. There are no clear borders between reality, dream and recollection. It is a quest for land in an infinite ocean, with crickets as the only support, and the memory of what once was ...
